room_title: Escape room "Crime Scene" by Murder Escape in Tulsa
room_description: A Hollywood starlet has met a fatal death. Such a young and beautiful life cut short. The crime scene holds the evidence to find the killer. Hidden behind all the glitz and glamour holds a truth of deception and lies. Your team has 60 minutes to locate the evidence and discover the killer, time of death, murder weapon and the motive.
